## Emergency Commands

```bash
# Save work immediately
git add . && git commit -m "WIP: Emergency save"

# See what's uncommitted
git status

# Undo last commit (keep changes)
git reset --soft HEAD~1

# Discard all changes (DANGEROUS!)
git reset --hard HEAD
```

